Package com.commercetools.api.models.product_selection

Class ProductSelectionSetVariantExclusionActionImpl

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.api.models.product_selection.ProductSelectionSetVariantExclusionActionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProductSelectionSetVariantExclusionAction, ProductSelectionUpdateAction, ResourceUpdateAction<ProductSelectionUpdateAction>, ModelBase
public class ProductSelectionSetVariantExclusionActionImpl extends Object implements ProductSelectionSetVariantExclusionAction, ModelBase

Updates the Product Variant Exclusion of an existing Product Selection Assignment. A ProductVariantExclusion can only be set if the Product has already been excluded from the Product Selection with IndividualExclusion ProductSelectionMode.

If the specified Product is not assigned to the Product Selection, a ProductAssignmentMissing error is returned.
